   - `heading-node.ts` — re-exports from StarterKit  
   - `list-node.ts` — re-exports from StarterKit
   - `code-node.ts` — re-exports from StarterKit
   - `quote-node.ts` — re-exports from StarterKit
   - `table-node.ts` — exports the Table + TableRow + TableHeader + TableCell configuration

