### Context

Frontend app at `apps/web/`. Uses React 18, TipTap v3.x (already installed).

**Extensions:** `apps/web/src/components/format-workspace/tiptap/extensions.ts` exports `extensions` array.

**Serializer:** `apps/web/src/components/format-workspace/tiptap/serializer.ts` exports:
